Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說棒冰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說Di-Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底收拾掉那幫傢伙的人是誰
