Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓拓  名名什麼都知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅告訴我Di-Sword的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  還有  real撲倒
